    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Approximately 20-40% of SARS-CoV-2 infection is asymptomatic; however, data are limited on drivers of such infection. Among over 730,000 SARS-CoV-2 test results in Los Angeles between August-October, 2020, we found heterogenous frequencies of asymptomatic infection among various sup-populations. Further research is needed to delineate drivers of asymptomatic SARS-CoV-2 infection.</jats:p>",
